\b HOME PAGE\b0\par
3. Search Option\par
3.1 User should see the availability of drivers in his/her area.\par
3.2 should provide a live location.\par
3.3 Cab driver details should be provided.\par
\par
4. Booking\par
4.1 Enter their destination to help in estimating the fare\par
4.2 View the available drivers, their information and the details of the car they drive\par
4.3 Cancel trips if necessary\par
4.4 Rate and add a tip for the driver if the service was great\par
4.5 View price estimates\par
4.6 Schedule a ride in advance\par
4.7 Add multiple drop-off points\par
4.8 Make payment for the trip they took\par
\par
5. Payment\par
5.1 After the trip the payment should be shown.\par
5.2 It should provide an option to pay extra as a tip for the driver.\par
5.3 Provide an option for UPI/ debit or credit card payment.\par
5.4 A invoice should be provided to the customer with riding distance,time duration and amount of ride.\par
\par
6. Feedback\par
6.1 Show the customer a feedback page.\par
6.2 Customer is needed to provide rating for the driver if he/she likes the ride or not.\par
6.3 Book the driver if interested for next ride.\par
6.4 Provide a review of the driver by the customer.\par
\par
7. My profile\par
7.1 List all details of user's full name ,email,phone number,age....etc\par
7.2 Edit profile link to edit profile page\par
7.3 sign out button\par
\par
\f1 8. Track booking\par
8.1 \fs22 A Customer shall be able to track the booking before it reaches him/her.\par
8.2 A Customer shall see the phases from booking to delivery included: Waiting for confirmation, Confirmed, Preparation, Delivery.\par
8.3 A Customer shall view details of the booking.\par
8.4 A Customer shall be able to cancel the order before the delivery phase.\par
